Package: python-gpstime
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python:Depends},
 python-dateutil,
Description: GPS-aware Python datetime module
 Provides a gpstime class that extends the built-in datetime class to
 include GPS time conversion methods.  Leapsecond information is
 synchronized from the IETF.

Package: python3-gpstime
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 ${python3:Depends},
 python-dateutil,
Description: GPS-aware Python3 datetime module
 Provides a gpstime class that extends the built-in datetime class to
 include GPS time conversion methods.  Leapsecond information is
 synchronized from the IETF.
 .
 Python3 compatibility.

Package: gpstime
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 python-gpstime,
Description: GPS time conversion utility
 Command line utility for converting to/from GPS time.  Uses the
 gpstime Python module.
